{"id":47613,"title":"Extracorporeal membrane oxygenation support after Ivor-Lewis esophagectomy for esophageal adenocarcinoma.","abstract":"Respiratory failure after Ivor-Lewis esophagectomy results in poor outcomes. Limited treatment strategies are available to manage this severe complication. One possibility is extracorporeal support. We report the successful use of extracorporeal support as a successful strategy for refractory respiratory failure. ","date":"2014-03-03","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24580930","annotations":[{"name":"Extracorporeal membrane oxygenation","weight":0.901385,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Extracorporeal_membrane_oxygenation"},{"name":"Respiratory failure","weight":0.821646,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Respiratory_failure"},{"name":"Esophagus","weight":0.774151,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esophagus"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.684428,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Respiratory system","weight":0.684152,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Respiratory_system"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.606559,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Esophageal cancer","weight":0.470702,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esophageal_cancer"},{"name":"Oxygenation (medical)","weight":0.300546,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxygenation_(medical)"},{"name":"Cell membrane","weight":0.242293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cell_membrane"},{"name":"Adenocarcinoma","weight":0.213142,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adenocarcinoma"},{"name":"Esophagectomy","weight":0.208635,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esophagectomy"},{"name":"Extracorporeal","weight":0.0537772,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Extracorporeal"},{"name":